						               													<description>A press-your-luck dice game where you earn chips based upon the results of rolling four dice. Every time you roll two or more matching dice, you earn chips. You can choose to reroll as many times as you like to earn more chips but as soon as your roll shows no matches, you bust and lose the chips you earned that turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When you bust, roll a single die and note the number, then select one of the upright cups from the center of the table. Either keep the cup for yourself or give it to another player. Whoever takes the cup flips it upside down and either loses, gains, or steals chips equal to the number rolled. Play continues until all cups are flipped over (with a special rule for the last cup). The player with the most chips wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
